Employee Id           : 329
Paid Leaves Per Year  : 20
Working Days Per Week : 5
Final Salary (US)     : 16000.0
Leave Balance = 10

*******INDIAN EMPLOYEE DETAILS*******

Name                  : Guru
Employee Id           : 315
Paid Leaves Per Year  : 25
Working Days Per Week : 6
Final Salary (INR)    : 5000.0
Leave Balance = 10
